        <h1>About Bright Cave Digital</h1>

        <p>
          Bright Cave Digital is a digital growth studio built on a simple idea:
          not every business needs the same kind of help. Some want to learn and
          do it themselves. Some want a guide alongside them. Others just want it
          handled.
        </p>

        <h2>Our approach</h2>
        <p>
          We organise everything we do around three tiers — Do It Yourself, Done
          With You, and Done For You — so you can choose the level of support that
          fits your budget, timeline, and appetite for hands-on work.
        </p>

        <h2>Why "Bright Cave"?</h2>
        <p>
          A cave is where you go to focus and do deep work; the bright part is the
          clarity we bring to it. We turn the murky, overwhelming world of digital
          marketing into something clear and actionable.
        </p>

